{
  "name": "RPlog_Dangerous_Decisions",
  "title": "Dangerous Decisions",
  "summary": "In the New Republic barracks on Calamari, the musician Paul Nighman finds the street kid Shenner restless and despondent after deciding to enlist with the Republic under General Calhoun. What begins as a casual voice lesson grows increasingly charged as Paul's hands-on coaching leaves Shenner visibly distressed and trembling, until a weary Jessalyn arrives and gently sends Paul away to give the girl space. Walking outside with Jessalyn, Paul listens to her confess that she must flee to a new posting on Yavin to escape the Sith Lord and her own torment, and the two share a tender, intimate moment of friendship. Realizing how deeply his earlier rejection wounded Shenner, mirroring his own past heartbreak, Paul resolves to commit to her. He returns to the barracks, offers Shenner a place at his side, and kisses her, and through her shock and tears she begins, haltingly, to believe him.",
